1. *Mogućnost* da se promeni rutina je veoma bitna. (The possibility to change the routine is very important.)

2. Nema *mogućnosti* da se izbegne situacija. (There is no possibility to avoid the situation.)

3. On je bio uveren da će ići na put, ali se ispostavilo da nema *mogućnosti*. (He was sure he was going on a trip, but it turned out there was no possibility.)

4. *Mogućnost* da steknemo dodatna znanja je vrlo dobra. (The possibility to gain additional knowledge is very good.)

5. Iako ima puno prepreka, postoji *mogućnost* da se postigne uspeh. (Although there are many obstacles, there is a possibility to achieve success.)